                  <a href="#comment-596812" name="comment-596812">February 23, 2017 at  8:28 pm</a>
                  <p>I haven&rsquo;t been in Haifa yet; when I was a teenager learning Hebrew in Brazil, my teacher was a lady from Haifa. She used a method with us (mishpachat Doron). This was in the 80&rsquo;s: I remember there was a lesson in which Mishpachat Doron characters were going to &ldquo;Kolnoa Armon&rdquo;; then our teacher explained us this was a very traditional cine theater there.</p>
                
                  <p>Sorry it was demolished.Sorry.</p>
